title: Olympic gold medal swimmers in Goshen
text: Posted Oct. 14, 2015 at 4:31 PM Updated at 4:39 PM Posted Oct. 14, 2015 at 4:31 PM Updated at 4:39 PM Â» Social News Olympic gold-medal winning swimmers Ryan Lochte, Missy Franklin, Natalie Coughlin and Cullen Jones were in Orange County to shoot a Speedo commercial at Goshen Sports Complex's swimming pool. The commercial will air on NBC during the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro. recordonline.com Posted Oct. 14, 2015 at 4:31 PM Updated at 4:39 PM
